# Claude Rules

Please follow the guidelines and rules defined in the `.junie/` directory:
- `.junie/instructions.md` (Process and consent)
- `.junie/coding_rules.md` (Coding standards: Simplicity, useEffect avoidance, etc.)

**Conflict Resolution:**
If any rule in the `.junie/` directory contradicts a rule defined here in `.clauderules`, the rule in `.clauderules` takes precedence.
